Manage the global moss daemon

Usage: moss daemon [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  status  Show daemon status
  stop    Stop the daemon
  start   Start the daemon (background)
  run     Run the daemon in foreground (for debugging)
  add     Add a root to watch
  remove  Remove a root from watching
  list    List all watched roots
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json       Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>  Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty     Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact    Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help       Print help
